description:
OK, here is one of those guys that make you go "hmmmmm...."

Keith is 22 and he says he is straight.

Remember, I'm just the messenger!

He says he has a girlfriend, but has "done it" with another guy. And by "done it" he means, "everything except intercourse."

Where did he meet his hookup? In a gay bar.

"Are you more into guys or girls?" we asked.

"Girls," he said. "The guy thing was a long time ago."

However, he admits that if he was single, he would "entertain" the idea of putting his dick up another guy's butt!
title: Keith
